    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":5530,"title":"NWACC Receives Grant To Launch Trails Trade School","topic":"Education ","slug":"nwacc-receives-grant-to-start-trails-trade-school","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/253803f4ba5f184f462983fd8c0a96cf/cc0b4a9fdf00fa165975df1d32164dec.jpeg"},"photoCredit":"NorthWest Arkansas Community College","date":"2023-01-12","content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.nwacc.edu/default.aspx\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">NorthWest Arkansas Community College</a> has received an $8m grant on behalf of the <a href=\"https://www.waltonfamilyfoundation.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Walton Family Foundation</a> to develop a trade school program for trail building and maintenance.</p><ul><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">New industry</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: The Trails Trade School will develop a workforce of </span><a href=\"https://www.5newsonline.com/article/money/nwacc-foundation-use-grant-establish-trails-trade-school/527-5616d2fb-7fa4-4891-8a0f-9910404594ee\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">certified trail technicians</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> to serve our growing community's dependence on the network of regional trails for transportation and recreation. </span></li><li><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Skilled</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">: Along with gaining a certification in trail building and maintenance, Trails Trade School students can gain certification in NWACC's </span><a href=\"https://www.nwacc.edu/workforce/bicycletechnician/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Bicycle Technician Program</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"> or earn an associate degree in </span><a href=\"https://www.nwacc.edu/workforce/constructiontechnology/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Construction Technology</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">. </span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Read more on the story </span><a href=\"https://www.nwaonline.com/news/2023/jan/10/8-million-grant-to-get-trails-school-going-at/?fbclid=IwAR1doPm0GEb6s5BgZxeYAGlnnxjQ9AMGobCF_xvTCeOkI52fz1_0HnWE6wc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">HERE</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">. </span></p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"nwacc-receives-grant-to-start-trails-trade-school"}},
